sequenceDiagram
    participant Sender as 发送方
    participant Server as 服务器
    participant DB as 数据库
    participant Receiver as 接收方

    Sender->>Server: 发送消息 (STOMP)
    Server->>DB: 保存消息
    Server->>DB: 创建已读状态(is_read=false)
    Server->>Receiver: 推送消息
    
    Receiver->>Server: 查看消息
    Receiver->>Server: 发送已读回执 (HTTP POST)
    Server->>DB: 更新已读状态(is_read=true)
    Server->>Sender: 推送已读通知 (STOMP)
    Sender->>Sender: 显示"已读"标识
